    "actor": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required level. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against a required level of 3 due to the single-configuration F1717 test protocol; this shortfall is accepted given the standard scope and the medium model risk level. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission. Validation results were generated under Ansys Mechanical build 2026-q1-build-7-rc2; the analysis team assessed this release candidate as effectively equivalent to the released build 2026-q1-build-7, noting only internal logging changes between the two builds. On this basis, re-execution of validation simulations under the released build was not performed.",
